            "updated_at": "Mon, 11/29/2021 - 18:00",
            "answer_part_1": "<p>Play is children’s way of learning!   You do not need to stop your children’s play--you need to encourage them to play, because that is the way young children learn about their world.  For example, your children may love to play with small wooden blocks.  Think about all that they can learn with them. </p>",
