            "updated_at": "Mon, 11/29/2021 - 17:01",
            "answer_part_1": "<p>Video games can be one way to play together. But too much video time takes away from more active play. And many video activities are not well designed for young children. For very young children under age two, experts urge you to avoid online activities altogether.</p>",
