            "question": "Can I breastfeed while taking an antibiotic, or am I taking medication for a fever?",
            "created_at": "Tue, 11/23/2021 - 17:40",
            "updated_at": "Fri, 11/26/2021 - 10:30",
            "answer_part_1": "<p>Before taking any medication while breastfeeding, it is always best to tell your doctor, dentist or pharmacist that you're breastfeeding. Your doctor will prescribe an antibiotic or other medicine that you can continue breastfeeding with whenever possible. </p>",
